#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:3
msgid "System"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:5
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`System` tab at the Render context of the Properties Window, "
"let the game developer specify options about the system performance "
"regarding to frame discards and restrictions about frame renderings, the key"
" to stop the Blender Game Engine, and whether to maintain geometry in the "
"internal memory of the Graphic card."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:12
msgid "Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:16
msgid "System tab at the Render Context"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:20
msgid "Use Frame Rate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:20
msgid ""
"When checked, this will inform Blender whether to run freely without frame "
"rate restrictions or not. The frame rate is specified at the "
":guilabel:`Display` tab of the :guilabel:`Render` Context of the Properties "
"Window. For more information about frame rates, see the :doc:`Display "
"</game_engine/performance/display>` page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:23
msgid "Display Lists"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:23
msgid ""
"When checked, this will tell Blender to maintain the lists of the meshes "
"geometry allocated at the GPU memory. This can help to speed up viewport "
"rendering during the game if you have enough GPU memory to allocate geometry"
" and textures."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:26
msgid "Restrict Animation Updates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:26
msgid ""
"When checked, this will force Blender game engine to discard frames (even at"
" the middle of redrawing, sometimes causing *tearing* artifacts) if the rate"
" of frame rendered by the GPU is greater than the specified at the "
":doc:`Display </game_engine/performance/display>` Tab."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:29
msgid "Exit Key"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/game_engine/performance/system.rst:29
msgid ""
"Clicking at this button will ask the user to type a key to specify a key to "
"stop the game engine from running."
msgstr ""
